&lt;Bevis Industries Inc> said itretained Tucker Anthony and R.L. Day Inc to seek purchasers ofthe company or its units.    It issued no further details.    The company, which makes stainless steel tubing for thechemical, petrochemical, and oil industries, earned 1,045,000dlrs or 51 cts a share in the nine months ending September 30,1986. It had sales of 17.1 mln dlrs in the period. Reuter&#3;